onsive. It times out and turns itself off when it does not detect any movement within a range of 2.5 meters, and it immediately comes back on when anyone enters the room. This feature not only saves on your electric bill but makes the frame easier to use overall. Once you set it up, there is no reason to change any settings unless you want to add photos.","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/scrn/small/52129-nix-8-hu-motion-frame10.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kNqurMQBhdAc4RYRAQniqM.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"kNqurMQBhdAc4RYRAQniqM","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/kNqurMQBhdAc4RYRAQniqM.jpg","alt":""},"id":"5e6efcf2-c290-4fa5-85b0-5363f83af950","type":"image"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["The motion sensor is just one reason this digital photo frame earned the highest possible score for ease of use in our digital picture frame evaluation. Another great feature is the easy-to-use remote control that allows you to tab through photos from across the room."]},"id":"d70eeefc-0cd4-46f4-944f-104fa7104787","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Specifications"},"id":"d54d0524-7bed-421f-8cb7-6fe6f0cf1300","type":"heading"},{"data":{"path":"/N2XzgEpxSwJ5bkNvHA73ka.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/scrn/small/52129-nix-8-hu-motion-frame13.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/N2XzgEpxSwJ5bkNvHA73ka.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"N2XzgEpxSwJ5bkNvHA73ka","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/N2XzgEpxSwJ5bkNvHA73ka.jpg","alt":""},"id":"aae9f567-b2fc-49ad-b909-2d10db648e84","type":"image"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Although it is not connected to the internet for easy access to Netflix or other video content, the NIX X08D can accommodate video that you have on USB, SD and SDHC cards. Video is easier than ever to record these days, so you may have as many videos as you do photos. This frame allows you to enjoy them on a nice big screen rather than on your cell phone.","This is a very versatile frame in terms of slideshows. You can decide from 13 different ways to transition from one slide to another. This is not a huge issue for everyone, but it is a nice way to personalize the photo display. You can decide whether photos fade gradually or change quickly.","One drawback with this frame is the lack of any internal memory. You can use camera cards and jump drives to display a large collection of photos, but none of them are ever stored on this electronic picture frame, which is somewhat inconvenient. It does make this frame especially simple to use, though. All you have to do is plug in your storage device.","This is not the best frame for a wall display either. There are no pre-drilled holes in the frame that would make it easy to hang. It&#39;s perfectly at home on a desk, countertop or shelf, though."]},"id":"e3949398-0f39-451c-bf5e-01c4b4da7f8f","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Display"},"id":"5b952004-618d-4000-b39a-fc39f872bab8","type":"heading"},{"data":{"path":"/mASobQ5D8z9qvaTWG9W3M9.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"Nixplay is strong in terms of customer support. Its people are really proactive about it. There is no waiting for a response to an email question for days. There is a live chat window on the site that is actually live a lot of the time. Someone responds quickly to just about any question you can think of about Nixplay&#39;s frames. You can also reach its people over the phone if you prefer.","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/scrn/small/52129-nix-8-hu-motion-frame12.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mASobQ5D8z9qvaTWG9W3M9.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"mASobQ5D8z9qvaTWG9W3M9","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mASobQ5D8z9qvaTWG9W3M9.jpg","alt":""},"id":"3098cd16-bd7a-4da6-ad99-f83e3bdba787","type":"image"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"8505e856-0b9a-43a7-809a-c3d23501bf70","type":"heading"},{"da